descriptionHTML:
Beware. Now Illuminati are watching you.

Download now the official Illuminati watchface on your Android Wear device. Do so and you'll please Illuminati. They will repay you with their super high protection.

To apply and sponsor Illuminati campaign to take over the world, go into your Android Wear companion app and select it from the menu, or simply long-press on your watch to select.

Supports square and round screens. Ambient mode and Burn-in protection activated.
